OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Ffine, albeit breezy, evening with some
OL,7,Flate sunshine. A few showers arriving
OL,8,Facross Cumbria later with perhaps the
OL,9,Fodd one elsewhere across the region
OL,10,Fovernight. Winds easing but staying
OL,11,Fbreezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA mainly dry though often
OL,14,Frather cloudy day, with a chance of
OL,15,Fshowers, these mainly in the morning.
OL,16,FQuite breezy and feeling fresher,
OL,17,Fthough still pleasant when the sun
OL,18,Fappears.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
