OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FAfter a
OL,6,Fchilly start, Sunday looks likely to
OL,7,Fbe dry with some sunshine. Somewhat
OL,8,Fcooler on Monday and Tuesday as a
OL,9,Fnortheasterly breeze introduces more
OL,10,Fcloud and the odd shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
